<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Ry Jeso Tompo soa,
 Ry Vatolampiko !
 Esory avokoa
 Ny hevi-dratsiko.
 Omeo ahy hery,
 Arovy tsy ho very
 Ny ondry kelinao,
 Mba hifalianao ;
 Jesosy ô ! henoy re, henoy.</lyrics>
<title>Ry Jeso Tompo soa FFPM343</title>
<author>Fr. Abt</author>
